{"tid":1414370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少一個敵人 多一個同路","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T23:59:50.000Z","uid":271843,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fa52982f5863b22a8354dc3a4ad59f79a06c3960","tid":1414370,"uid":271843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:08:48.000Z","msg":"梁天琦獄中書說過「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠</span></span></span></span>。」<br />\n<br />\n明白堵路真的不是示威者責任，是林鄭政府從沒有回應訴所致<br />\n<br />\n亦明白面對藍絲廢老，真係想大把大把車落去。<br />\n<br />\n但在堵路及開口罵人之前，<br />\n想一想<br />\n我要的是一時之勇，還是抗爭勝利<br />\n<br />\n如果我們<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輸掉這場戰爭</span></span>，文的武的，就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等如對過去幾名犧牲者，被捕那200名義士之不顧</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n為了他們，想一想<br />\n圍可以，衝可以，要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準中共在港黨羽</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n那些不明不白，之今也保持中立的奴化港人，<br />\n我們不當他們是同路也不要推向敵方"},{"pid":"b3fcc0d91596ec6afd91c599339b7077c4ad6ddd","tid":1414370,"uid":271843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b9f5afdf707c95d22b7d5c3a7368a935bf22b8ec","tid":1414370,"uid":32150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4036cee369c99fa05c974061c7eb0cfb3fd790a","tid":1414370,"uid":271843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:01:44.000Z","msg":"沒有民意支持的革命<br />\n<br />\n與今天共產黨無異"},{"pid":"30bb54dd127fcefa8103c8103838c8e7a38a1a2a","tid":1414370,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:06:51.000Z","msg":"咁多議辦唔去參觀下?"},{"pid":"0051de1e67daaf76f7574ed853d8a8918892b6fb","tid":1414370,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"66497db1c0ff4000615f2cf73da30dab86644120","tid":1414370,"uid":271843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30bb54dd127fcefa8103c8103838c8e7a38a1a2a","tid":1414370,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:06:51.000Z","msg":"咁多議辦唔去參觀下?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"去去去"},{"pid":"cd9931a6eacde6efe3a03369ee90bafedcf51fb0","tid":1414370,"uid":271843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}